    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything feels so heavy and exhausting. the counselors, the tasks, the small steps... it all just feels like a performance. i'm tired of pretending that there's some hidden meaning behind just existing. it feels like i'm just waiting for the lights to go out, and honestly, i don't see why i should fight it so hard. it's just so lonely being here by myself.",
